===== Script =====

This class is designed to work with scripts. 

Object references: \\
  * [[manual:api:reference:script:object#script|Script]]

Available methods: \\

  * ''[[manual:api:reference:script:create|script.create]]'' - create new scripts
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:script:delete|script.delete]]'' - delete scripts
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:script:execute|script.execute]]'' - run scripts
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:script:get|script.get]]'' - retrieve scripts
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:script:getscriptsbyhosts|script.getscriptsbyhosts]]'' - retrieve scripts for hosts
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:script:update|script.update]]'' - update scripts